description:
Anywhere Auction:
Registered Link - https://anywhereauctions.com.au/app/property?propertyId=28608

Nested in a quiet block of units, this freshly painted 2-bedroom unit ticks all the boxes whether you're a first home buyer, investor, or a downsizer looking for a low-maintenance lifestyle. Two good-sized bedrooms with robes, neat kitchen, spotless bathroom/laundry, with great timber floor, individual carport, and a minimal maintenance private Front yard for party and relaxation.

The unit also consists of split system heating and cooling, a gas upright heater, and much more! A big advantage to the buyer is the location, everything is at your doorstep. Walking distance to Westall Station, Westall Primary School, Westall High School, Rosebank Avenue eateries, and surrounding parklands. A short drive to Monash University, IKEA, and Clayton Shops. A must inspect, don't miss out, units like these are getting harder to find!

Don't waste another minute, call or text Shanky Walia on 0434 781 294 texts or emails shanky.walia@raywhite.com to inspect today.
